'''Ngwarati''' (''sable'' in English) imuka yemusango iri mumhuri ye[[nhoro]]. Mhuka iyi ine ruvara rwutema (black) nedumbu jena (white). pachiso chayo ine mutandamhno mutema nemitsetse mitema inobva kumaziso ichienda kumuromo. Muromo wepasi unennge uri muchena. Ngwarati ine nyanga dzakasvonaka dzine tesva dzichidzokera kumashure.

==Tsika==

"Zvaiwana ngwarati"  - kureva kuti uya anombozviti ndini ndinogona zvamuwanawo nhasi.

Chikwata cheRubgy cheZimbabwe chinodanwa kunzi "Sables" - iriyo ngwarati.

